open_long: |
  Opening a long position on {{token}} with {{leverage}}x leverage via GMX.
  Your position will execute on Arbitrum for low fees.
  Make sure you understand the risks of leverage.

open_short: |
  Opening a short position on {{token}} with {{leverage}}x leverage.
  Shorting is risky — your position can be liquidated if the price goes up.

close_position: |
  Closing your active perp position.
  This will return your margin to your wallet.
